  "time_ut": 1660898466,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Burial is allowed in the cemetery",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A resolution has been unanimously passed in the Norwood Pradeshiya Sabha to continue to use the burial ground which has been used for the burial of the dead by the people of Vanaraja area - Darawala Colony under the Norwood Pradeshiya Sabha.",
        "The monthly meeting of the Norwood Pradeshiya Sabha was held yesterday (18) under the chairmanship of the Chairman of the Council, Mr. Ravi Kuddavelu, at Dinsin Mandapam.",
        "During this, Samarvil Local Member M. Ramachandran presented a special motion regarding Hatton-Tikoya Municipal Council's refusal to allow the bodies of the dead to be buried in the public cemetery, which has been used by the people of Darawala Kolani under Vanaraja District for burying their dead.",
        "It is saddening that Hatton \u2013 Dikoya Municipal Council Chairman and Dikoya District Municipal Council member could not give permission to bury the body of Kathirvel who died yesterday (17) evening in the public cemetery where the people were burying the deceased in Darawala Colony under the jurisdiction of Norwood Pradeshiya Sabha.",
        "The Norwood Parish Council should provide appropriate redress to Annarath's family who have been affected by this inhuman act.",
        "The victims told me that while arrangements have been made for cremation of the body of the deceased today (18) at 03 in the evening, it is now 11.30 a.m. Till this time Hatton-Tikoya Municipal Council has refused permission to cut a burial pit in the burial ground and there are only three and a half hours left.",
        "Burial land can be transferred to the local council or city council and cannot be owned. On behalf of the Norwood Parish Council, I express my strong condemnation of this action by the Hutton-Tikoya City Council and express my condolences to the affected family.",
        "He said that the said graveyard is an area under the jurisdiction of Norwood Pradeshiya Sabha, so Norwood Pradeshiya Sabha is allowing the use of the cemetery which has been used by the people of Darawala Colony until now and today I am giving permission to bury Anna's body in the same graveyard.",
        "After this was supported by all the members who participated in the meeting, the resolution was passed that the people of Darawala Colony under Vanaraja will continue to use the same burial ground."
      ],
